===
    - ORB
         - Simplify network address retrieval code.
         - Protect against OutOfMemory in GIOPConnection::receiveMessages to prevent client hanging.
         - Handle reconnecting via a closed connection to a persistent server (BZ975).
         - Fix for local interceptors and slots (BZ976)
         - Simplify logging.
         - Fix for CodeSet tag appearing twice in multi-profile IORs
         - Deprecate defining org.jacorb.orb.standardInterceptors.IORInterceptorInitializer as a
           standard interceptor; it is now implicitly defined by jacorb.codeset QoS.
