         - Codeset configuration : by default they are now enabled.
         - Fix for port / endpoint initialisation.
         - Fix for ORB instances sharing Current information.
         - Fixed SSL properties reading and processing (BZ#820).
         - Improve SAS Error propagation (and add tests).
         - Removed unused GSSUP code.
         - Fix for forward request handling for special operations (BZ#979)
         - Fix for connection closure/server restart with multiple connections (BZ#986)
         - Move Singleton debug code into Diagnostic class to avoid JDK issues.
         - Improve ordering of network addresses.
         - Fix for creation of corbaloc with IPv6
         - Fix internal ordering of ORBEndpoints
         - Fix for interceptors and restarted server (BZ#983)
    - Documentation
        - Minor fixes.
